      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i'm flying into heathrow tomorrow and need to get to edinburgh. i was thinking of taking the heathrow express to kings cross then switching to an lner train. how much buffer time should i leave between the heathrow express getting in and the lner train leaving? i dont want to miss the connection if there's a delay.",
